```plantuml
@startuml IBM_ios-mapkit-indoor-map

actor User

participant "iOS App\n(ViewController.swift)" as iOSApp
participant "Backend\n(app.js)" as Backend
database "MongoDB" as Database

User -> iOSApp: Open App
iOSApp -> iOSApp: Initialize Map
iOSApp -> Backend: GET /maps/floorplan
Backend -> Database: Fetch Floorplan PDF
Database --> Backend: Floorplan PDF
Backend --> iOSApp: Floorplan PDF

iOSApp -> iOSApp: Render Floorplan
iOSApp -> Backend: GET /events/heatmap
Backend -> Database: Fetch Heatmap Data
Database --> Backend: Heatmap Data
Backend --> iOSApp: Heatmap Data

iOSApp -> iOSApp: Generate Heatmap Overlay
User -> iOSApp: Interact with Map
iOSApp -> iOSApp: Convert Coordinates

User -> iOSApp: Trigger Event
iOSApp -> Backend: POST /events/trigger
Backend -> Database: Store Event
Database --> Backend: Acknowledge Event
Backend --> iOSApp: Confirmation

@enduml
```